Personal Tax rate for Individuals

Income Level (NPR) Tax Rate (FY 2020-21) Taxable Amount
Up to 4 lakh 1% NRP 4,000
Additional 1 lakh 10% NRP 14,000
Additional 2 lakh 20% NRP 54,000
Next 1,300,000 30% NRP 444,000
Additional Tax: Above 2,000,000 36% NRP 624,000
